    "name": "JR Tower Hotel Nikko Sapporo",
    "detail": "The hotel location is superb. The room although a little but small but as a typical japan. This would consider average. However, the view is fabulous ( try all 4 sides and still like everyside) The service staff has no flaw here. I can only think of few other hotels that has a more impressive service than this one (those are not in hokkaido and also come with ridiculously expensive price). The breakfast is average to 5 stars level The hot spring is nice consider this in the middle of sapporo (of couse you can not compare with ryokan that located in natural onsen area) Overall, it is the best hotel in sapporo in term of quality, No matter you are business man, couple, or family. ",
